--[[
    author:
        d1sasterpiece - 26/08/2023

    amended:
        29/08/2023 - adding support for tracking parts, gun attachments and ammo
        30/08/2023 - mcm support for changing the colour of all compatible item highlights
        02/09/2023 - adding support for tracking repair tools
                   - adding support for localizing menu strings
        07/09/2023 - Removing use of SYS_GetParam for parent_section
                     For some reason using this caused another addon (outfit overhaul) to crash when hovering over exoskeleton
                     No idea why this was the case - but swapping for "ini_sys:r_string_ex" fixes it
                     Perhaps a caching issue based on function internals

    name:
        track compatible item upgrades

    description:
        Adds tracking capability to guns and armour so that any compatible upgrades in any bags
        are highlighted
]]

